# Claude Code project adapter

Before any project work, read `WIKI.md` and `research.md` in full.

- `WIKI.md` is the only canonical source for project rules, variant, schemas, and workflow constraints.
- `research.md` is the shared project context, progress log, scope, and current TODO list.
- Project-local workflows live in `.claude/commands/` and `.claude/agents/`.
- If this file conflicts with `WIKI.md`, follow `WIKI.md`.

Do not add project or business rules here. Update `WIKI.md` instead so Claude Code and Codex stay aligned.
